e spent on previously unheard of amounts of red paint for cycle lanes on roads that are too small in a city with no alternative transport conduits.<\/p>\n<p>This month I am also highlighting <a href=\"http:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/FinnMcDonald?feature=watch\">the Finn McDonald YouTube channel<\/a> on which one can find (a decreasing number of) long YouTube videos containing the music produced in soundtrack recording sessions, including <a href=\"http:\/\/www.g400.co.uk\/cantabits\/archives\/1466\">my favourite music<\/a>. A number of films with good soundtracks are covered by the channel.<\/p>\n<p>In other news I remain quite busy but I have recently finished off and scheduled a few posts that I started many months ago.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The website of the month for October 2013 is A view from the cycle path. The website seems to be primarily about cycling as a means of transportation but also has some posts specific to the problem of cycling in &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.g400.co.uk\/cantabits\/archives\/1826\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[12,46,8],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.g400.co.uk\/cantabits\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1826"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.g400.co.uk\/cantabits\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.g400.co.uk\/cantabits\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.g400.co.uk\/cantabits\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.g400.co.uk\/cantabits\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1826"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.g400.co.uk\/cantabits\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1826\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.g400.co.uk\/cantabits\/wp-js